addToPrepaid(uint256).details: ERC20 approve needs to be done

appointeeVote(address,uint256).details: need to be appointee, set by staker themselves

params._petId: : id of PET in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this PET.

params._petId: : id of PET in staket address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has PET

params._token: : is EraSwap ERC20 Smart Contract Address

params._minimumMonthlyCommitmentAmount: : minimum PET monthly amount in exaES

params._petId: : id of PET in staket address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has PET

returns._0: current month of a particular PET

params._petId: : id of PET in staket address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has PET

params._annuityMonthId: : this is the month for which timestamp to find
params._petId: : id of PET in staker address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has a PET

params._endAnnuityMonthId: : this is the month (inclusive) to stop at
params._petId: : id of PET in staker address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has a PET
params._startAnnuityMonthId: : this is the month (inclusive) to start from

makeDeposit(address,uint256,uint256,bool.details: ERC20 approve is required to be done for this contract earlier if prepaidES   is not selected, enough funds must be there in the funds bucket contract   and also deposit can be done by nominee

params._petId: : id of PET in staker address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has a PET

makeLumSumDeposit(address,uint256,uint25.details: lum sum deposit is possible in the first month in a fresh PET

params._petId: : id of PET in staker address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has a PET
params._totalDepositAmount: : total amount to deposit for 12 months

params._monthlyCommitmentAmount: : PET monthly commitment amount in exaES
params._planId: : id of PET in staker portfolio

sendPrepaidESDifferent(address[],uint256.details: some ES already in prepaid required

params._addresses: : address array to send prepaid ES for PET
params._amounts: : prepaid ES for PET amounts to send to corresponding addresses

params._newAppointeeStatus: : true or false, should this have appointee rights or not.
params._petId: : id of PET in staker portfolio.

params._newNomineeStatus: : true or false, whether this should be a nominee or not.
params._petId: : id of PET in staker portfolio.

updatePlanStatus(uint256,bool).details: pets already initiated by a plan will continue only new will be restricted

params._planId: : select a plan to make it inactive

params._petId: : id of PET in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this PET.

returns._0: tells whether this address is a appointee or not

params._petId: : id of PET in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this PET.

returns._0: tells whether this address is a nominee or not

params._endAnnuityMonthId: : this is the month upto which benefits to be withdrawn
params._petId: : id of PET in staker address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has a PET

params._petId: : id of PET in staker address portfolio
params._powerBoosterId: : this is serial of power booster
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has a PET
